title: Readout of Vice President Biden's Calls on Libya | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Vice President


For Immediate Release
March 20, 2011

 



Readout of Vice President Biden's Calls on Libya




The Vice President spoke today to Prime Minister of Algeria Ahmed Ouyahia and Emir of Kuwait Sheikh Sabah Al-Ahmad Al-Jaber Al-Sabah as part of the ongoing consultations on the coalition action to fulfill United Nations Security Council Resolution 1973.Â  The Vice President discussed with both the Prime Minister and the Emir their mutual support for the full implementation of the resolution and the need to protect the Libyan people.
